Package: shinymath
Title: Mathematical Input for Shiny Apps (One Line, Title Case)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Tomas",
           family = "Capretto",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "tomicapretto@gmail.com")
Description: This package provides mathematical input function based on Mathquill. 
  With this input, the users of your shiny apps can write mathematical equations
  that can be passed to the app server as LaTeX code, R code or even an R function.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
